Third Department,

January, 1944.

(January 12, 1944.) In the Matter of the Claim of Gretchen E. Schneider, Respondent, against Archie Baxter's Flying Service, Inc., et al., Appellants, and Aggregate Trust Fund of the State Insurance Fund, Respondent. State Industrial Board, Respondent.

Motion for reargument denied. Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied, without costs. [See 266 App. Div. 1037.] Hill, P. J., Bliss, Heffernan and Sehenck, JJ., concur.
